    "comment": "Rationale: Synapsin I KO mice are viable and show no effect on basal synaptic transmission. Mice lacking synapsin I exhibit a selective increase in paired pulse facilitation, with no major alterations in other synaptic parameters such as long-term potentiation.. Experimental description: M&M: Generationof Murine Synapsin I Null Mutants by Homologous Recombination In ES Cells. tandard procedures were used to record synaptic responses from hippocampal slices prepared from control and mutant mice.",
